import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    
    plt.hist(data['delay'], bins=50, color='blue', alpha=0.7, label='Flight Delays')
    plt.axvline(data['delay'].median(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label=f"Median: {data['delay'].median():.2f}")
    
    plt.xlabel('Delay (minutes)')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of flight delays?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    
    average_delay = data['delay'].mean()
    
    plt.hist(data['delay'], bins=50, color='blue', alpha=0.7)
    plt.axvline(average_delay, color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label=f'Average Delay: {average_delay:.2f}')
    
    plt.xlabel('Delay (minutes)')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the average delay time for flights?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    
    delay_by_origin = data.groupby('origin')['delay'].mean().sort_values(ascending=False)
    delay_by_destination = data.groupby('destination')['delay'].mean().sort_values(ascending=False)
    
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(12, 6))
    ax.bar(delay_by_origin.index, delay_by_origin.values, alpha=0.6, label='Origin')
    ax.bar(delay_by_destination.index, delay_by_destination.values, alpha=0.6, label='Destination')
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    plt.xlabel('Airport')
    plt.ylabel('Average Delay (minutes)')
    plt.title('Which airports have the most delays?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
